msgctxt "68_Receptionist"
msgid "Hello, sir. This is your first time here, right? Then allow me to explain the rules."
msgstr "Hello, sir. This is your first time here, right? Then allow me to explain the rules."

msgctxt "80_Receptionist"
msgid "Aromatherapy Massage is a minigame where you rapidly press buttons to keep the gauge from going past the top or the bottom. If it does, you lose the game."
msgstr "Aromatherapy Massage is a minigame where you rapidly press buttons to keep the gauge from going past the top or the bottom. If it does, you lose the game."

msgctxt "92_Receptionist"
msgid "The gauge is divided into five parts. The higher the gauge goes, the more points you earn. Go for the most points possible by keeping the gauge as high as you can without letting it go past the top or the bottom."
msgstr "The gauge is divided into five parts. The higher the gauge goes, the more points you earn. Go for the most points possible by keeping the gauge as high as you can without letting it go past the top or the bottom."

msgctxt "104_Receptionist"
msgid "If you make it to the end without letting the gauge go past the top or bottom, the Finish Gauge appears on the center of the screen. You win if you fill up this gauge before time runs out. Note that the gauge is harder to fill if you scored too few points earlier."
msgstr "If you make it to the end without letting the gauge go past the top or bottom, the Finish Gauge appears on the center of the screen. You win if you fill up this gauge before time runs out. Note that the gauge is harder to fill if you scored too few points earlier."

msgctxt "116_Receptionist"
msgid "Okay, which massage would you like?"
msgstr "Okay, which massage would you like?"

msgctxt "140_Receptionist"
msgid "Hello, sir. Which massage would you like today?"
msgstr "Hello, sir. Which massage would you like today?"

msgctxt "176_Player"
msgid "I'll have the Standard Massage."
msgstr "I'll have the Standard Massage."

msgctxt "212_Player"
msgid "I'll go for the Deluxe Course today."
msgstr "I'll go for the Deluxe Course today."

msgctxt "248_Player"
msgid "I'll do the VIP Oil Massage."
msgstr "I'll do the VIP Oil Massage."

msgctxt "284_Player"
msgid "I'll do the Super VIP Massage Course."
msgstr "I'll do the Super VIP Massage Course."

msgctxt "320_Receptionist"
msgid "All right. Since it is your first time using our services, we will start a member stamp card for you."
msgstr "All right. Since it is your first time using our services, we will start a member stamp card for you."

msgctxt "344_Receptionist"
msgid "Every time you use our services, you will earn one stamp. With enough stamps, you can unlock special massage options."
msgstr "Every time you use our services, you will earn one stamp. With enough stamps, you can unlock special massage options."

msgctxt "356_Receptionist"
msgid "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."
msgstr "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."

msgctxt "380_Receptionist"
msgid "All right. Let me stamp your member card."
msgstr "All right. Let me stamp your member card."

msgctxt "428_Receptionist"
msgid "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."
msgstr "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."

msgctxt "440_Receptionist"
msgid "Congratulations! Now that you've earned five stamps, our shop recognizes you as one of our special VIPs!"
msgstr "Congratulations! Now that you've earned five stamps, our shop recognizes you as one of our special VIPs!"

msgctxt "452_Receptionist"
msgid "You'll now have the choice of experiencing our VIP Massage Course on top of your other options. It'll make you feel even more refreshed and relaxed than ever! We hope you enjoy it."
msgstr "You'll now have the choice of experiencing our VIP Massage Course on top of your other options. It'll make you feel even more refreshed and relaxed than ever! We hope you enjoy it."

msgctxt "464_Receptionist"
msgid "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."
msgstr "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."

msgctxt "476_Receptionist"
msgid "Congratulations! Now that you've earned ten stamps, our shop recognizes you as one of our Super VIPs!"
msgstr "Congratulations! Now that you've earned ten stamps, our shop recognizes you as one of our Super VIPs!"

msgctxt "488_Receptionist"
msgid "You'll now have the choice of experiencing our Super VIP Massage Course on top of your other options. This incredible massage will take your body to Paradise! We hope you enjoy it."
msgstr "You'll now have the choice of experiencing our Super VIP Massage Course on top of your other options. This incredible massage will take your body to Paradise! We hope you enjoy it."

msgctxt "500_Receptionist"
msgid "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."
msgstr "Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."

msgctxt "572_Player"
msgid "(.................)"
msgstr "(.................)"

msgctxt "584_Therapist"
msgid "Hi! I hope you weren't waiting long!"
msgstr "Hi! I hope you weren't waiting long!"

msgctxt "608_Mari"
msgid "I'm Mari, and I'll be your massage therapist for this session. I look forward to working with you today! ♪"
msgstr "I'm Mari, and I'll be your massage therapist for this session. I look forward to working with you today! ♪"

msgctxt "620_Mari"
msgid "Follow me, please!"
msgstr "¡Sígueme, por favor!"

msgctxt "644_Mari"
msgid "Hey! I'm so glad to see you again! I'm gonna make sure you get lots of special attention today... Hehehe."
msgstr "Hey! I'm so glad to see you again! I'm gonna make sure you get lots of special attention today... Hehehe."

msgctxt "656_Mari"
msgid "Follow me, please!"
msgstr "¡Sígueme, por favor!"

msgctxt "680_Player"
msgid "(...Shoot, I don't have enough on me.)"
msgstr "(Maldita sea. No llevo suficiente dinero encima)"

msgctxt "704_Player"
msgid "Sorry, I just remembered something I need to do."
msgstr "Sorry, I just remembered something I need to do."

msgctxt "716_Receptionist"
msgid "All right. We hope to see you again soon."
msgstr "All right. We hope to see you again soon."

msgctxt "752_Receptionist"
msgid "All right! Boy, the Super VIP Course is really something, let me tell you."
msgstr "All right! Boy, the Super VIP Course is really something, let me tell you."

msgctxt "764_Receptionist"
msgid "I hear you'll experience a pleasure unlike anything anyone has ever experienced on this Earth."
msgstr "I hear you'll experience a pleasure unlike anything anyone has ever experienced on this Earth."

msgctxt "776_Player"
msgid "A pleasure... unlike anything..."
msgstr "Un placer... a diferencia de todo..."

msgctxt "788_Receptionist"
msgid "That's right! It's very rare for someone to get the opportunity to experience this kind of service. To be honest, I'm a bit jealous!"
msgstr "That's right! It's very rare for someone to get the opportunity to experience this kind of service. To be honest, I'm a bit jealous!"

msgctxt "800_Player"
msgid "It's... that amazing? *gulp*"
msgstr "Es... ¿Tan increíble? *trago*"

msgctxt "812_Receptionist"
msgid "Believe me, you can't even imagine the kind of pleasure you're about to... Oh, sorry, I got a little too excited there. We'll be ready for you soon, so please have a seat in the waiting room."
msgstr "Believe me, you can't even imagine the kind of pleasure you're about to... Oh, sorry, I got a little too excited there. We'll be ready for you soon, so please have a seat in the waiting room."

msgctxt "884_Player"
msgid "(...A pleasure unlike anything anyone has ever experienced on this Earth...)"
msgstr "(...A pleasure unlike anything anyone has ever experienced on this Earth...)"

msgctxt "896_Therapist"
msgid "I hope you weren't waiting long!"
msgstr "¡Espero que no hayas esperado demasiado!"

msgctxt "908_Player"
msgid "(...Here we go.)"
msgstr "(...Allá vamos.)"

msgctxt "932_Therapist"
msgid "Hi there! I'm Momiyama, and I'll be your massage therapist. I'm sooo excited to work with you today! ♪ Hehe, hehehe..."
msgstr "Hi there! I'm Momiyama, and I'll be your massage therapist. I'm sooo excited to work with you today! ♪ Hehe, hehehe..."

msgctxt "944_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "956_Receptionist"
msgid "Oh, you're so lucky, sir!"
msgstr "Oh, you're so lucky, sir!"

msgctxt "968_Receptionist"
msgid "Momiyama-san's one of the best massage therapists in the world! His incredible techniques won him a special prize in the world championships!"
msgstr "Momiyama-san's one of the best massage therapists in the world! His incredible techniques won him a special prize in the world championships!"

msgctxt "980_Receptionist"
msgid "I hope you're looking forward to the ultimate pleasure you're about to experience! Boy oh boy, am I jealous of you!"
msgstr "I hope you're looking forward to the ultimate pleasure you're about to experience! Boy oh boy, am I jealous of you!"

msgctxt "992_Player"
msgid "Ultimate... pleasure..."
msgstr "Último... placer..."

msgctxt "1004_Momiyama"
msgid "Wow, your body is divine! Like a Greek god, chiseled from the purest marble... I can't wait to work my magic on it. Hehehe..."
msgstr "¡Vaya, tu cuerpo es divino! Como un dios griego, cincelado en el mármol más puro... No puedo esperar para hacer mi magia en ello. Jejeje..."

msgctxt "1016_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1028_Receptionist"
msgid "I'll see you when you're back from heaven!"
msgstr "¡Te veré cuando regreses del cielo!"

msgctxt "1040_Receptionist"
msgid "All right! Please take a seat in the waiting room while we prepare your room."
msgstr "¡Muy bien! Por favor, siéntese en la sala de espera mientras preparamos su habitación."

msgctxt "1112_Player"
msgid "(......................)"
msgstr "(......................)"

msgctxt "1124_Momiyama"
msgid "I hope you weren't waiting long!"
msgstr "¡Espero que no hayas esperado demasiado!"

msgctxt "1148_Momiyama"
msgid "Hiii, I'm Momiyama! So good to meet you! Hehehe... Don't worry, I'm going to make sure you get lots of special treatment, my succulent Hercules!"
msgstr "¡Hola, soy Momiyama! ¡Es un placer conocerte! Jejeje... ¡No te preocupes, me aseguraré de que recibas un trato muy especial, mi suculento Hércules!"

msgctxt "1160_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1172_Momiyama"
msgid "Right this way! Don't be shy, now!"
msgstr "¡Venga por aqui! ¡No seas tímido, ahora!"

